        "rich_text_yEyBJV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>At<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Lucira Jewelry\"> Lucira Jewelry</a>, ring designs focus on balance -  highlighting the beauty of the center diamond while ensuring the ring feels comfortable and modern.</p><p>Our solitaire and halo rings are crafted using IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, offering brilliance while supporting responsible sourcing.</p><p>Whether someone chooses a clean solitaire ring, a hidden halo design, or a classic halo setting, the goal remains the same: creating jewellery that feels timeless and personal.</p>",
